title: 在更新神奇宝贝3.3.6的时候的问题
author: shiguang
txt_content:
我的1.7.10服务器 在更新3.3.6神奇宝贝mod的时候  上传完毕 点击开服  会出现这样一段
19.12 15:38:39 [Server] ERROR Unidentified block: pixelmon:Dawnstone_Ore, id 246
19.12 15:38:39 [Server] ERROR Unidentified block: pixelmon:Duskstone_Ore, id 443
19.12 15:38:39 [Server] INFO new mapping pixelmon:Duskstone_Ore
19.12 15:38:39 [Server] INFO missingmap pixelmon:Duskstone_Ore
19.12 15:38:39 [Server] INFO new mapping pixelmon:Dawnstone_Ore
19.12 15:38:39 [Server] INFO missingmap pixelmon:Dawnstone_Ore
19.12 15:38:39 [Server] INFO new mapping pixelmon:Dawnstone_Ore
19.12 15:38:39 [Server] INFO missingmap pixelmon:Dawnstone_Ore
19.12 15:38:39 [Server] INFO new mapping pixelmon:Duskstone_Ore
19.12 15:38:39 [Server] INFO missingmap pixelmon:Duskstone_Ore
19.12 15:38:39 [Server] INFO Processing missing mappings
19.12 15:38:39 [Server] INFO Found a missing id from the world pixelmon:Duskstone_Ore
19.12 15:38:39 [Server] INFO Found a missing id from the world pixelmon:Dawnstone_Ore
19.12 15:38:39 [Server] INFO Found a missing id from the world pixelmon:Dawnstone_Ore
19.12 15:38:39 [Server] INFO Found a missing id from the world pixelmon:Duskstone_Ore
19.12 15:38:39 [Server] INFO Injecting existing block and item data into this server  
然后就开不了服务器  大概是因为删除了3.3.5版本的2种矿石吧  有人知道怎么解决吗？ 我相信不我一个人开神奇宝贝服务器
大家都会遇到吧！  求解答
